title: Udyr Special

embed.description: Playing Udyr jungle in Season 6 patch 6.10 haha, he is super fun to play!, went with Runic Echoes this time, it is very good to clear jungle creatures really quickly, but would love to try full ad or even full ap some day!

body:
Hey guys, made a little Funtage :D, Hope you guys enjoy!!

Any bit of feedback is appreciated :)!
